  "title": "🦅💖 Event & Telco Sales Marketing Ambassador 🏆",
  "description": "<p>🚀 Join Our Growing Telco Sales Team!</p>\n<p>Represent one of Singapore’s <strong>top telco brands</strong> through <strong>face-to-face marketing</strong> at roadshows, events, and residential outreach.</p>\n<p>💼 What We Offer:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>📈 <em>Unlimited earning &amp; growth potential</em></li>\n  <li>🏢 Work with leading MNCs in the telco industry</li>\n  <li>🧠 Full training provided – no experience? No problem!</li>\n  <li>🛫 Overseas exposure &amp; team trips<br>\n<em>(Melbourne, Malaysia, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Indonesia, Korea, Thailand)</em></li>\n  <li>🤝 Team-based environment — never solo!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>👀 We’re Looking For:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>🎓 Fresh grads / ORD personnel / Career switchers</li>\n  <li>💪 Fast learners with leadership potential</li>\n  <li>🔥 Go-getters who want personal growth</li>\n  <li>💬 Strong communicators who adapt quickly</li>\n  <li>🤜🏼🤛🏽 Able to work independently <em>and</em> with a team</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📌 Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>📣 Face-to-face sales &amp; product presentations</li>\n  <li>📞 Promote telco services &amp; assist customers</li>\n  <li>💡 Provide excellent service &amp; solutions</li>\n  <li>🔄 Adapt to changes &amp; stay proactive</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🇸🇬 <strong>Open to Singaporeans &amp; PR only</strong></p>\n<p>🎯 Ready to start your journey in sales, grow your value, and have fun doing it?</p>\n<p><strong>Apply now and level up with us!</strong></p>",
